data.description: This property offers two separate homes. Discover a unique mixed-use space in the heart of Old Town Glendale. You can possibly use the main home storefront for your business and also live there. The casita can be used for extended family or as a way to earn extra money. The interiors have been fully updated with a modern touch. The living room and kitchen are open, creating a spacious and cozy atmosphere. The property also features a front porch, a grassy backyard, and a walkway between the two homes. Assumable FHA Loan with Low Interest Rate of 2.875%! Enjoy a nice walk to Glendale Glitters from this Historic Landmark Jonas McNair House. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own a space that offers endless possibilities.
